{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"永远向着毛主席","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":9}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远向着毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔藏族民歌三首〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论是刮风、下雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕你天阴、落雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大金寺的塔顶呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永久是亮晶晶的！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不论是千辛、万苦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕你千难、万难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"藏族人民的心呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远向着毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中也在歌唱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪山闪银光；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有月亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路亮堂堂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草青、水甜、牛羊肥壮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有共产党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们在梦中也在歌唱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"警惕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蛇皮很美丽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是它有毒牙齿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海螺很漂亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是肚子里弯弯曲曲！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天的头人很和气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是怀里揣着刀子！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻了身的农奴兄弟呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你随时要睁大眼睛！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}